{"title":"不通过数据卷在docker容器与宿主机间交换数据","date":"2020-03-21T13:36:03.000Z","link":"copy-files-from-docker-container","comments":true,"tags":["docker"],"categories":["tools"],"updated":"2022-01-04T08:35:48.567Z","content":"<p>通常情况下，我们让docker容器与宿主机进行文件传输，最好的方式就是使用挂载数据卷，但偶尔会遇到一些特殊的情况，容器没有挂在数据卷，但容器内又保存着重要的数据，我们希望将它移到宿主机上，但关闭容器重新挂载数据集又会丢失这些数据，为此我们需要一个方法让宿主机和已经启动的容器间能够交换数据。</p>\n<p>本文介绍docker的 <code>cp</code> 复制指令。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"将本地文件复制到docker容器内\">将本地文件复制到docker容器内<a href=\"copy-files-from-docker-container#将本地文件复制到docker容器内\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span> sudo docker cp &lt;path-in-localhost&gt; &lt;container-id&gt;:&lt;path-in-container&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"将docker容器内的文件复制到本地\">将docker容器内的文件复制到本地<a href=\"copy-files-from-docker-container#将docker容器内的文件复制到本地\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span> sudo docker cp &lt;container-id&gt;:&lt;path-in-container&gt; &lt;path-in-localhost&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"频谱分析","link":"computer-vision-spectral-analysis"},"next":{"title":"卷积(Convolution)","link":"computer-vision-convolution"},"plink":"https://yuxinzhao.net/copy-files-from-docker-container/","toc":[{"title":"将本地文件复制到docker容器内","id":"将本地文件复制到docker容器内","index":"1"},{"title":"将docker容器内的文件复制到本地","id":"将docker容器内的文件复制到本地","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Yuxin Zhao","link":"<a href=\"https://yuxinzhao.net/copy-files-from-docker-container/\" title=\"不通过数据卷在docker容器与宿主机间交换数据\">https://yuxinzhao.net/copy-files-from-docker-container/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}